            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;This wizard will walk you through converting {!Get_person_details.FirstName} into their own household.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The process cannot be undone and you should only do this when finances are to be separated out.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The following changes will occur:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;New household created for &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;{!Get_person_details.FirstName} &lt;/span&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;They&#39;ll be a client in this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The current household will no longer be their primary one&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;This means they can&#39;t own products or assets in it etc&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The financial products for &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;{!Get_person_details.FirstName} will be copied to their new household&lt;/span&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;Any Junior products will be converted to regular ones (e.g. JISA to ISA)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;Their financial products in the parent&#39;s household will be closed and disappear from their views in the profile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ql-cursor&quot;&gt;﻿&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
